OL,5, A petition to introduce a legal duty of
OL,6, care from universities and colleges    
OL,7, towards their students will be debated 
OL,8, by MPs on Monday afternoon.            
OL,10,FThe debate was called after signatures 
OL,11,Fon the petition, started by 25 families
OL,12,Fwhose children killed themselves while 
OL,13,Fat university, exceeded 100,000.       
OL,15,FThey want the existing duty of care for
OL,16,Fstaff to also cover adult students.    
OL,18,FBut both the government and the higher 
OL,19,Feducation sector say further           
OL,20,Flegislation would be disproportionate. 
